                    <lb xml:id="p3-l14"/>Sonnenberg zu <placeName type="place" key="Hirslanden (Zürich)">Hirslanden</placeName> <lb xml:id="p3-l15"/> am <date when="1854-04-16">16. April
				1854</date>.</p>
      </div>
